songs.title: Brain Zapped
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Mom always said that books could take you to another world
But I don't think that this is what she meant
(This is what she meant)
I'm shuttling through these distant lands and ocean shores
Don't really know where I'll go next
'Cause I've been...

[Chorus]
Brain Zapped
Let’s go explore
Brain Zapped
To a whole new world
Brain Zapped
Come be my guest
Brain Zapped
Don't know where I'll go next

[Verse 2]
My mind is spinning around
Got all this knowledge
I just want to shout out
Got to get it under control
Because the light is green, and we're ready to go
(Go, go)

[Chorus]
Brain Zapped
Let’s go explore
Brain Zapped
To a whole new world
Brain Zapped
Come be my guest
Brain Zapped
Don't know where I'll go next
